data.oai_dc:dc: *BEAST v1.8.2 input file used for phylogenetic inference of Mabuyinae, using mitochondrial and nuclear DNA sequence data. Mitochondrial loci include ND2 and 16S, and nuclear loci include regions of BDNF, BRCA1, BRCA2, CMOS, EXPH5, KIF24, MC1R, MXRA5, and RAG1 protein coding genes. Includes DNA sequence data for 14 mabuyine and 2 outgroup taxa.
